OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778069461
OL,3,CFormer council leader guilty of sex
OL,4,Coffences against young men jailed
OL,6,FA former SNP council leader who was
OL,7,Ffound guilty of multiple sex offences
OL,8,Fagainst young men and teenagers has
OL,9,Fbeen jailed for 18 months.
OL,11,FJordan Linden, 30, resigned as the
OL,12,Fleader of North Lanarkshire Council in
OL,13,FJuly 2022 after reports of alleged
OL,14,Fsexual harassment emerged, leading to
OL,15,Fthe collapse of the SNP administration
OL,16,Fin the area.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/4
