OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778069461
OL,3,CFormer council leader guilty of sex
OL,4,Coffences against young men jailed
OL,6,FLinden, who left the SNP in 2024, was
OL,7,Fconvicted of 10 separate offences in
OL,8,FMarch following a trial at Falkirk
OL,9,FSheriff Court, including five sexual
OL,10,Fassaults.
OL,12,FHe was also found guilty of charges
OL,13,Finvolving sexual communication and of
OL,14,Fengaging in a course of conduct
OL,15,Fcausing fear or alarm.
OL,17,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,18,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,19,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,20,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/4
