PN,30303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778069461
OL,3,CFormer council leader guilty of sex
OL,4,Coffences against young men jailed
OL,6,FThe offences spanned the period 2011
OL,7,Fto 2021 and took place at locations in
OL,8,FNorth Lanarkshire and elsewhere.
OL,10,FLinden was jailed for 18 months when
OL,11,Fhe appeared at Falkirk Sheriff Court
OL,12,Fon Wednesday and placed on the sex
OL,13,Foffenders' register for 10 years.
OL,15,FFollowing the conviction, First
OL,16,FMinister John Swinney ordered an
OL,17,Findependent review of the SNP's
OL,18,Fprocesses in the wake of concerns
OL,19,Fabout the handling of complaints
OL,20,Fagainst Linden.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/4
